    "And it should be even worse for someone to traffic in misinformation.",
    "If someone cheated on their CV, they could be fired, even years after the offense.",
    "So too, there should be little tolerance for handing in homework with misinformation, especially when it is so easy to fact-check with search.",
    "It should not be the teacher's responsibility to fact-check the homework.",
    "To discourage the spread of misinformation, there need to be prohibitively high penalties in the court of public opinion for trafficking in misinformation."
